Producer Side

KafkaTemplate → Used to send messages to Kafka topics.

ProducerFactory → Creates Kafka Producer instances.

DefaultKafkaProducerFactory → Default implementation that creates Kafka producers.

StringSerializer → Converts String keys into bytes before sending to Kafka.

JacksonJsonSerializer → Converts Java objects into JSON before sending to Kafka.

BOOTSTRAP_SERVERS_CONFIG → Specifies the Kafka broker address.

ADD_TYPE_INFO_HEADERS → Controls whether Java class type information is added to Kafka message headers.

topic → Logical channel where messages are stored and consumed.

send() → Publishes a message to a Kafka topic.